Package: rpigpior
Type: Package
Title: Provides R with Access to the Raspberry Pi
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Mark Niemann-Ross
Authors@R: 
    person("Mark", "Niemann-Ross", , "mark@niemannross.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3381-4604"))
Maintainer: Mark Niemann-Ross <mark@niemannross.com>
Description: This provides R with access to the Raspberry Pi General Purpose 
    Input Output (GPIO) including GPIO pins, i2c, and SPI. No additional libraries need to be installed; Raspbian includes 
    'libgpiod' as part of the standard installation.
URL: https://github.com/mnr/rpigpior,
    https://mnr.github.io/rpigpior/
BugReports: https://github.com/mnr/rpigpior/issues
